      "retweeted_tweet_id": null,
      "text": "ILLEGAL ALIEN CHARGED WITH RAPE WHILE TRAINING AS A CORRECTIONS OFFICER SET FREE BY PRISON\n\nIbrahim George Kallon, an illegal alien from Sierra Leone whose visitor visa expired in 2024, was arrested while training to be a Delaware County Prison corrections officer and charged by Glenolden Police for:\n\n—Rape\n—Involuntary deviate sexual intercourse\n—Sexual assault\n—Aggravated indecent assault\n—False imprisonment\n—Indecent assault\n\nDelaware County Prison sent him back into the community despite an ICE immigration detainer, so ICE @EROPhiladelphia officers had to arrest him at-large Feb. 11.\n\nIf the county won’t protect its own residents, we’ll do it for them.",
      "text_resolved": "ILLEGAL ALIEN CHARGED WITH RAPE WHILE TRAINING AS A CORRECTIONS OFFICER SET FREE BY PRISON\n\nIbrahim George Kallon, an illegal alien from Sierra Leone whose visitor visa expired in 2024, was arrested while training to be a Delaware County Prison corrections officer and charged by Glenolden Police for:\n\n—Rape\n—Involuntary deviate sexual intercourse\n—Sexual assault\n—Aggravated indecent assault\n—False imprisonment\n—Indecent assault\n\nDelaware County Prison sent him back into the community despite an ICE immigration detainer, so ICE @EROPhiladelphia officers had to arrest him at-large Feb. 11.\n\nIf the county won’t protect its own residents, we’ll do it for them.",
